{"tid":1290094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲警方拘7名中國遊客　疑在墨爾本「職業行乞」","createTime":"2019-07-06T11:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T11:14:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"624afe95385498c50fcbf37ae2e8d29e050571f4","tid":1290094,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"澳洲警方在墨爾本市中心，拘捕7名持旅遊簽證入境的中國遊客，懷疑他們是「職業乞丐」，在當地行乞。警方表示，估計被捕人士已將部分行乞所得的款項兌換成人民幣，他們有地方居住，並非弱勢群體。警方又表示，澳洲民眾雖然慷慨，但不會容忍這些人的行為。<br />\n<br />\n有警員說，這些中國遊客同屬一個犯罪集團，集團成員曾以旅遊簽證的身份到澳洲，並假裝無家可歸，然後將行乞獲得的金錢送到海外。<br />\n<br />\n墨爾本市長對事件感到驚訝，呼籲民眾不要直接拖捨行乞者，應幫助他們尋求協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466921-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466921-20190706.htm&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=6a114f2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466921-20190706.htm&h=211a23de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466921-20190706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"59744fd6cb9faa57307c454a236feeeab34dc26e","tid":1290094,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"十香港有冇拉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9afec85af84082b23d4ff0bb715ef79277f9511","tid":1290094,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59744fd6cb9faa57307c454a236feeeab34dc26e","tid":1290094,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"十香港有冇拉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"香港唔敢拉"}]}